rows.label: qst003301_msg0001
rows.name:
Meh meh meh?
What you say?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0002
rows.name: Shatoto is illegal resident?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0003
rows.name:
Nobody live here!
Shatoto has no moneycoins for inn.
Just take little nap!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0004
rows.name:
Besides, when Shatoto come to town,
soldiers say "give money!" and Shatoto
pay residence fee like good citizen.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0005
rows.name:
Huh? Meh?
Why surprise?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0006
rows.name:
Meh meh! No need residence fee
to enter town?!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0007
rows.name:
Shatoto was duped...
Shatoto's beautiful money, all gone...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0008
rows.name:
Meeeeeh... Shatoto's long-desired foods
were finally available in Gula...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0009
rows.name:
Wanted to use money from Mamapon
to buy delicious foods...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0010
rows.name: Shatoto is sorry, Mamapon!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0011
rows.name:
Meh? Friends will bring delicious
foods for Shatoto?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0012
rows.name:
Yay!
Yay!
Happy times!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0013
rows.name:
When Shatoto was littlepon, he met
man called Ahato in Avaritia.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0014
rows.name:
Ahato become very fond of local
delicacy of Noodle Soup at that time.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0015
rows.name:
Shatoto want to try Torigo Noodle
Soup, so here Shatoto is!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0016
rows.name:
Many years pass, and Shatoto not
littlepon anymore. Wonder if Ahato still
making Noodle Soup...?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0017
rows.name:
But Shatoto has no money, so if go to
noodle place, all he hear is "no noodles
for Shatoto" and other sad things.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0018
rows.name:
If Shatoto could eat Noodle Soup of
Ahato, Shatoto would be able to go
back to home, full-tummy smiley.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0019
rows.name:
Friends are the first nice people
Shatoto has met.
Soldiers are too shouty scary...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0101
rows.name:
Avaritia Noodle Soup with
Torigo flair...
What could taste be like?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0102
rows.name:
Shatoto has never eaten Torigo
foods so difficult to imagine.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0103
rows.name: So hungry...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0201
rows.name:
Tummy is rumbly grumbly... Meh!
What is delicious smell?

rows.label: qst003301_msg0202
rows.name:
Ruska Noodle Soup?
So this is Torigo-style
Noodle Soup invented by Ahato!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0203
rows.name:
It look totally different to
Avaritia Noodle Soup.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0204
rows.name: Come to Dadapon!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0205
rows.name:
*slurp* *gulp*
*gulp* *slurp*

rows.label: qst003301_msg0206
rows.name: Ahhh.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0207
rows.name:
Tinglyhot soup...
Chewysoft noodles...
Crispycrunch veggies...

rows.label: qst003301_msg0208
rows.name:
This is delicious evolution of
Avaritia Noodle Soup from
childhood of Shatoto!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0209
rows.name:
It was very yummy!
Thank you, friends.
Ahhh!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0210
rows.name:
Thank you.
Shatoto will have happy memories
of this day.

rows.label: qst003301_msg0211
rows.name:
Shatoto will save so he can
bring Mamapon here and
feed delicious noodles!

rows.label: qst003301_msg0212
rows.name:
Sorry about sleeping here!
Shatoto will head home now.
